        <div class="col container-fluid m-3 py-3">
            <h1 style="font-size: 4.5vh; margin-bottom: 30px;">Submit an Official Academic Transcript</h1>
            {{#if tasks.task4}}
            <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" role="button" href="/task/complete/task4"> Task Completed</a>
            {{else}}
            <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" role="button" href="/task/complete/task4"> Click to Complete Task</a>
            {{/if}}
            <p style="margin: 30px 0px;">In your home country, submitting your high school or university transcripts to
                universities you’d like to attend
                might be fairly straightforward. However, as you make yourself known to US universities, you’ll want to
                be sure they
                can correctly interpret the transcripts that reflect all your hard work at your previous institutions.
            </p>

            <div class="accordion m-4" id="accordionExample">
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingOne">
                        <button class="accordion-button text-dark" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                            data-bs-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseOne">
                            <h2 style="font-size: 3.5vh">What are transcript evaluations?</h2>
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" aria-labelledby="headingOne"
                        data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            <p>The education system in your home country is likely very different from the education
                                system in the US. For this
                                reason, US educational institutions often use transcript evaluations. A transcript
                                evaluation is a document that
                                will allow US academic institutions to understand your academic record from your home
                                country. It helps answer
                                questions like, What types of institutions have you attended?What was the highest level
                                of education you completed?
                                What degrees have you earned? </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingTwo">
                        <button class="accordion-button text-dark collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                            data-bs-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
                            <h2 style="font-size: 3.5vh">What are Credential Evaluation Services? </h2>
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTwo"
                        data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            <p>Credential evaluation services are organizations that perform transcript evaluations for
                                students and professionals
                                from one country who intend to study in another country. Each university you wish to
                                attend will likely have
                                information on their admissions websites listing the credential evaluation services
                                whose evaluations they accept.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingThree">
                        <button class="accordion-button text-dark collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                            data-bs-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
                            <h2 style="font-size: 3.5vh">Can I choose an evaluation service myself?</h2>
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree"
                        data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            <p>In some cases, you will be allowed to choose the credential evaluation service you want
                                to use, but the educational
                                institution may require that your chosen evaluation service belong to a certain
                                association or organization. </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingFour">
                        <button class="accordion-button text-dark collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                            data-bs-target="#collapseFour" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseFour">
                            <h2 style="font-size: 3.5vh">You may not need an evaluation service after all</h2>
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="collapseFour" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingFour"
                        data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            <p>In still other cases, you may be required to send your official transcripts from your
                                home country directly to the US
                                educational institution, or you may simply be asked to enter your coursework information
                                yourself at some point
                                during the application process. If you are asked to provide the coursework information
                                yourself, in most cases you
                                will need to be sure that you are entering the information exactly as it is shown on
                                your official school records.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
